    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow employers to give staff non-taxable \u00a31000 cost of living payment",
        "additional_details": "This would cost the Government nothing and allows employers who can help to assist their staff in bearing the brunt of the cost of living crisis.",
        "background": "The Government should allow companies to pay staff a non-taxable cost of living allowance of \u00a31,000 each, over and above their usual salary. This should be free of all tax, Employers National Insurance and Class 1 National Insurance.",
